name: MyLog
0:

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my log
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill will Log an event with a timestamp in a Google Sheet. This allows you to log timestamps for any important events that you would like to keep track of when they occurred.

You can also ask when the last time you logged a specific action by saying "Alexa, ask my log when did I __?)

This skill will not be verified by Google, as I do not own www.google.com.

The Log Sheet will be named "My Log", and found in your Google Drive.
